{"tid":1076952,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我個朋友係咪比人包？","createTime":"2019-03-25T08:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T18:44:55.000Z","uid":46480,"like":29,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4148281a33525953e6ebff37067337e86ededb0f","tid":1076952,"uid":46480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:45:18.000Z","msg":"我有個朋友每個月都會去一次旅行話係同屋企人去<br />\n<br />\n有次佢啱啱去完旅行我去佢屋企，見到有個喼行李牌係另一個人既名，果個人名係佢舊公司director， 另一次就係見到張喼登機個貼紙，都係果個名<br />\n<br />\n見過佢wtsapp間唔中出現果個人名既shortform, 而每次佢話去trip前幾日一定會有<br />\n<br />\n去trip好突然，今日無啦啦會話聽日去trip,但之前完全無講<br />\n<br />\n呢啲徵狀係咪比人包緊？<br />\n所有野都係我自己直覺之後八掛然後無意發現，問佢又驚佢難堪fd都無得做，唔問我又自己好奇心爆發成日喺度諗<br />\n<br />\n應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9428411b84b9cb1cfdc639a2825e168c57ad4e73","tid":1076952,"uid":96743,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:46:43.000Z","msg":"關唔關你事？<br />\n比人包要問你攞Approval?<br />\n定你個fd有仔 有仔又唔同講法"},{"pid":"0d871404c7603c977ffc482dfbdfb0e066696054","tid":1076952,"uid":76527,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:46:58.000Z","msg":"人地做雞又要你批准<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d83515b87c2684e1ea6f2cd3819209942e0470b","tid":1076952,"uid":55758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:47:08.000Z","msg":"你個朋友比人包姐<br />\n<br />\n又唔係你自己比人包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18dc156d6b9ed1fe8082c4df6d10a2fab4deeae","tid":1076952,"uid":49648,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T08:50:38.000Z","msg":"當你有錢時，你就會明白，錢真係萬能的。<br />\n<br />\n3萬日本4天全包，大把靚女爭住做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b015eac66ef0b426fa06f00d6e2f4ccfc0